The Stripe customer is created and saved to the user document within the `placeOrder` function in `orderController.js` at line 8.

**Code**  
```js
File: backend\controllers\orderController.js | Line: 8
const placeOrder = async(req,res)=>{
    // ...
    let stripeCustomer;
    if (!user.stripeCustomerId) {
        const customer = await stripe.customers.create({
            name: user.name,
            email: user.email,
        });

        stripeCustomer = customer.id;

        // Save Stripe Customer ID in user database
